Contract Implementation The Contract will be for one (1) year from the date of Contract award with an irrevocable option to extend it for up to one additional one-year period.  The following expectations are included in these Requirements: (a) scheme-based device/user management; (b) multisource / multivendor KPIs measurement; and (c) conformance to industry compliance and security certification standards.  Solicitation  #1000395662 is a synopsis of a proposed contract for the Provision of "Provision of Hardware and Support for the uptake of Cyber Security Framework".   Award    Contract award will be made from a negotiated settlement.
